{"type": "article", "id": 22815, "title": "木质家具组", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-25T07:36:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122205c1BeRisQ3SuNwMOr.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">Stamford Smith Designs 是一家善于发掘自然材料的工作室，他们主要推出木制的桌椅和小件。除了保留木头本身的纹路外，还会在外形上刻意做出木头的凹凸感。用不同品种的木材拼成一张小桌是最常见的手法，做成深浅相间的条纹状，边缘也往往随之有了起伏的纹路，以突出它的分层。<a href=\"http://www.stamfordsmith.com/\">有兴趣可以点击这里查看工作室的设计。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222036y2DiLeNuvoGnBT7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.74166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122203XSVlsbnUPRO0e89a.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.495\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122203rvtNYFRbpBaEZx03.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122204JS7gAb1hiDcTUHGN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.495\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122204JviIExwa23WbNcus.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.495\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}